{"tid":1638246,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"Police Officers Are Charged \"Assault\" Rather Than \"Torture\"","createTime":"2019-10-08T08:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T18:09:11.000Z","uid":217844,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c81408938a47734a75b5a02c72034fceeac98068","tid":1638246,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/08/20/two-hong-kong-police-officers-arrested-torture-62-year-old-arrestee-hospital/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2Ftwo-hong-kong-police-officers-arrested-torture-62-year-old-arrestee-hospital%2F&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNhUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=791db435\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/08/20/two-hong-kong-police-officers-arrested-torture-62-year-old-arrestee-hospital/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3023564/shocking-video-shows-hong-kong-police-beating\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Flaw-and-crime%2Farticle%2F3023564%2Fshocking-video-shows-hong-kong-police-beating&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNhUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=8564c39b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3023564/shocking-video-shows-hong-kong-police-beating</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;In eight minutes of security camera footage from the June 26 incident &ndash; which was not related to the protest movement sweeping the city &ndash; two policemen are seen repeatedly hitting their 62-year-old male victim in the head, abdomen and genitals, in North District Hospital, Sheung Shui.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nAlthough the three polices have obviously committed &quot;torture&quot; (which is liable to LIFE imprisonment) , they were only charged &quot;assault&quot; instead (which is liable to imprisonment of <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">MAXIMUM 3 years</span></strong>)<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190822/59958981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190822%2F59958981&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNhUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=adb9499a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190822%2F59958981&h=8d969c53\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190822/59958981</a><br />\n(I can only find the source in Cantonese<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\nSee? The &quot;Separation of powers&quot;. A 18-year-old student being shot by police could be charged with rioting and assaulting police officer, whereas the police officers who clearly committed torturing was charged with &quot;assault&quot;.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Heung Gong Yan Faan Kong!</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ccca2e292e89a4e4172a186d263efc62c778995","tid":1638246,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"03b5a557b0420441ff94f817da86b79caf8f6904","tid":1638246,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ec47dfc81a80fb72c91c1db1004a34b19631f61","tid":1638246,"uid":300435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T08:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4125d594fe28646aa8542e603bc3c084fc9d0a","tid":1638246,"uid":217844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"